'''Potassium''' was a [[chemical element]]. Several compounds of potassium existed,<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Balance Point">''[[The New Jedi Order: Balance Point]]''</ref> including [[Radiation/Legends|radioactive]] [[Salt/Legends|salts]].<ref name="Goatgrass: The Tale of Ree-Yees">{{StoryCite|story=Goatgrass: The Tale of Ree-Yees|book=Tales from Jabba's Palace}}</ref> An overdose of the substance was [[Death/Legends|fatal]].<ref name="Do No Harm">{{JournalCite|10|Do No Harm}}</ref>

Potassium decayed, and this decay, when occurring within a [[Planet/Legends|planet]], heated the rock of the planet's crust.<ref name="Dark Forces: Soldier for the Empire">''[[Dark Forces: Soldier for the Empire]]''</ref>

